Mommy I prayed so hard and begged God from the bottom of my heart to restore your health. I’m sorry I couldn’t heal you myself!!! Nancy i don’t know how I’m going to keep going without your love and guidance. I can’t fathom not being able to see your face or hear your voice again. It’s not fair man!!!!!! You deserved to live a long healthy life, not for it to end this way. You were such a beautiful optimistic person despite any challenges that came your way! You fought this battle like a champ! Whew you put up a fight 💕You didn’t complain not 1 time nor did I see you down at any moment. I learned how to be a honorable woman because of you, But you never taught me how to live with your physical presence. Te amo mami I will miss you till my heart stops beating. Fly high in that realm full of light and wait for me please. Rest In Peace my courageous, beautiful mother, Nancy ❤️
